 Glass: Highball You’ll need: ½ cup orange tangerine juice; ½ cup sparkling apple juice; ½ cup natural ginger ale; 8 – 10 drops Angostura aromatic bitters How to: Combine ingredients in a small jug and stir. Serve over ice or straight up. Enjoy!  Glass: Highball You’ll need: 30ml freshly squeezed lemon juice; 22ml sugar syrup; 22ml lime cordial; 6 – 8 dashes of Angostura aromatic bitters; Lemonade; Garnish: fresh lemon or lime wedge How to: Add Angostura aromatic bitters, then ice. Add lemon juice, lime cordial and sugar syrup. Top up with lemonade. Garnish by squeezing the lemon/ lime wedge into the drink and serve.  Glass: Highball glass You’ll need: 165ml soda water; 165ml lemonade; 4 – 6 dashes Angostura aromatic bitters; Garnish: Fresh lemon or lime wedge How to: Build ingredients over ice, dash with Angostura aromatic bitters, stir and garnish with a lime wedge and serve. Follow @AngosturaZA on Facebook and Instagram for more mocktail recipes.